roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 1734862442, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1638085877, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1776707302851, "link": null, "locked": false}, {"id": "3e795b7b7989", "type": "text", "x": 3180, "y": 1060, "width": 520, "height": 245.0, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 1965757368, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 546875204, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1776707302851, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "JAMB raw rename mapping\n\nUTME Registration Number \u2192 utme_registration_number\nNIN \u2192 nin\nName of Candidate (First, Middle, Last) \u2192 candidate_name\nInstitution \u2192 institution\nYear of Admission \u2192 year_of_admission\nProgramme of Study \u2192 programme_of_study\nMode of Admission \u2192 mode_of_admission\nDisability Status of Candidate \u2192 disability_status_of_candidate\n\nLater in staging:\ninstitution \u2192 institution_name\ndisability_status_of_candidate \u2192 disability_status", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "JAMB raw rename mapping\n\nUTME Registration Number \u2192 utme_registration_number\nNIN \u2192 nin\nName of Candidate (First, Middle, Last) \u2192 candidate_name\nInstitution \u2192 institution\nYear of Admission \u2192 year_of_admission\nProgramme of Study \u2192 programme_of_study\nMode of Admission \u2192 mode_of_admission\nDisability Status of Candidate \u2192 disability_status_of_candidate\n\nLater in staging:\ninstitution \u2192 institution_name\ndisability_status_of_candidate \u2192 disability_status", "autoResize": true, "lineHeight": 1.25}, {"id": "8486987d3065", "type": "rectangle", "x": 2600, "y": 1210, "width": 540, "height": 370, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#495057", "backgroundColor": "#ffffff", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 1053720005, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1191861725, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1776707302851, "link": null, "locked": false}, {"id": "71c4e8cadcec", "type": "text", "x": 2610, "y": 1220, "width": 520, "height": 420.0, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 851114373, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1709689660, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1776707302851, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "UNICEF raw rename mapping\n\nID \u2192 id\nState \u2192 state\nLGA \u2192 lga\nWard \u2192 ward\nType \u2192 school_level_group\nSchool \u2192 school_name_raw\nNewSchoolCode \u2192 new_school_code\nLocation \u2192 location\nOwnership \u2192 ownership\nSchool Type \u2192 school_type\nP3_Male \u2192 p3_male\nP3_Female \u2192 p3_female\nP3_Streams \u2192 p3_streams\nP5_Male \u2192 p5_male\nP5_Female \u2192 p5_female\nP5_Streams \u2192 p5_streams\nJS2_Male \u2192 js2_male\nJS2_Female \u2192 js2_female\nJS2_Streams \u2192 js2_streams\nSS2_Male \u2192 ss2_male\nSS2_Female \u2192 ss2_female\nSS2_Streams \u2192 ss2_streams", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "UNICEF raw rename mapping\n\nID \u2192 id\nState \u2192 state\nLGA \u2192 lga\nWard \u2192 ward\nType \u2192 school_level_group\nSchool \u2192 school_name_raw\nNewSchoolCode \u2192 new_school_code\nLocation \u2192 location\nOwnership \u2192 ownership\nSchool Type \u2192 school_type\nP3_Male \u2192 p3_male\nP3_Female \u2192 p3_female\nP3_Streams \u2192 p3_streams\nP5_Male \u2192 p5_male\nP5_Female \u2192 p5_female\nP5_Streams \u2192 p5_streams\nJS2_Male \u2192 js2_male\nJS2_Female \u2192 js2_female\nJS2_Streams \u2192 js2_streams\nSS2_Male \u2192 ss2_male\nSS2_Female \u2192 ss2_female\nSS2_Streams \u2192 ss2_streams", "autoResize": true, "lineHeight": 1.25}, {"id": "239b9b714137", "type": "rectangle", "x": 3170, "y": 1330, "width": 540, "height": 300, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#495057", "backgroundColor": "#ffffff", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 1967305779, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1579264698, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1776707302851, "link": null, "locked": false}, {"id": "55bb0e9ca74f", "type": "text", "x": 3180, "y": 1340, "width": 520, "height": 157.5, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 300665461, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1344619981, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1776707302851, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "Critical business rules from source reality\n\n1. NBAIS candidate_address and candidate_type are currently empty \u2192 keep nullable.\n2. NBAIS blank subject grade = subject NOT written.\n3. NABTEB wide subject/grade slots must be unpivoted in staging.\n4. NECO and WAEC are candidate SUMMARY only; do not force subject-level marts for them.\n5. UNICEF is school-level only for now; keep separate from candidate marts.\n6. JAMB currently supports pipeline/admission analysis, not UTME score analysis.\n7. DOB is not clean enough to be the main cross-source matching key in phase 1.", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "Critical business rules from source reality\n\n1. NBAIS candidate_address and candidate_type are currently empty \u2192 keep nullable.\n2. NBAIS blank subject grade = subject NOT written.\n3. NABTEB wide subject/grade slots must be unpivoted in staging.\n4. NECO and WAEC are candidate SUMMARY only; do not force subject-level marts for them.\n5. UNICEF is school-level only for now; keep separate from candidate marts.\n6. JAMB currently supports pipeline/admission analysis, not UTME score analysis.\n7. DOB is not clean enough to be the main cross-source matching key in phase 1.", "autoResize": true, "lineHeight": 1.25}, {"id": "a70abcdb8e26", "type": "rectangle", "x": 1770, "y": 1340, "width": 780, "height": 330, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1c7ed6", "backgroundColor": "#eef7ff", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 1744610786, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1680167488, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1776707302851, "link": null, "locked": false}, {"id": "d93f1547c78c", "type": "text", "x": 1790, "y": 1355, "width": 700, "height": 30.0, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1c7ed6", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 1649270505, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 658030265, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1776707302851, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "7. RUN SEQUENCE TO EXPLAIN TO STAKEHOLDERS", "fontSize": 24, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "7. RUN SEQUENCE TO EXPLAIN TO STAKEHOLDERS", "autoResize": true, "lineHeight": 1.25}, {"id": "85928d901b45", "type": "text", "x": 1800, "y": 1400, "width": 720, "height": 140.0, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#495057", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 332694174, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 196040592, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1776707302851, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "1) Drop yearly file into landing folder or call API.\n2) Python ingestion loads source into the correct raw table with metadata.\n3) Great Expectations validates the loaded batch.\n4) Failed rows go to stg_quarantine_records; pipeline continues.\n5) dbt builds source-specific staging models.\n6) dbt builds conformed staging models.\n7) dbt builds marts for O-level participation, O-level performance, exam-to-tertiary pipeline, and UNICEF school profile.\n8) BI reads only from fme_nedi_marts.", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "1) Drop yearly file into landing folder or call API.\n2) Python ingestion loads source into the correct raw table with metadata.\n3) Great Expectations validates the loaded batch.\n4) Failed rows go to stg_quarantine_records; pipeline continues.\n5) dbt builds source-specific staging models.\n6) dbt builds conformed staging models.\n7) dbt builds marts for O-level participation, O-level performance, exam-to-tertiary pipeline, and UNICEF school profile.\n8) BI reads only from fme_nedi_marts.", "autoResize": true, "lineHeight": 1.25}], "appState": {"gridSize": null, "viewBackgroundColor": "#ffffff"}, "files": {}}